Generated Matter CodeÔÉÅ

The matter cluster library makes interaction objects easier to work with by providing cluster-defined structure, enum, and bitmap types, providing cluster constants, providing APIs for building InteractionRequests, and providing APIs for building test interaction Response objects for driver tests. It is generated from a zcl xml definition that exists in the project-chip/connectedhomeip repo.
